    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 147,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "这会为你的工作流程设置增加30-180秒，但能确保在构建开始时有最大的空间可用。"
  },
  {
    "row": 148,
    "rowsha": "0U8dI9HcMkNvRxpiEg/LR+LdWs6Kmerp0Bj60u3379s=",
    "originContent": "This adds 30-180 seconds to your workflow setup, but guarantees maximum space is available when your build begins.",
    "translatedContent": ""
